&gt;&gt; Hydras continue tracking Cyclonus and the others
&gt;
&gt; As Hydras approached he got finally into visual range of it, and he
&gt; could see that it was in truth a battle. Cyclonus&#39; striking form is
&gt; standing in the middle of it, his weapons lashing out. Even though he
&gt; seemed to firing rapidly in several different directions it is obvious
&gt; that he is being careful not to hit anything that would bring the
&gt; tunnel down on top of them.
&gt;
&gt; What Cyclonus is fighting was strange. It looked like some sort of
&gt; insect like creature, like a cross between a spider and a Mantis. It
&gt; had 10 legs, 6 for walking and 4 that ended in long sharp mantis like
&gt; claws. However instead of a living chitinous shell, it was encased in
&gt; yellow, red and orange armor, which looked disturbingly similar to
&gt; Rodimus&#39; armor style. They were rocket launchers and laser cannons
&gt; sitting on their frames, showing that they were definitely designed
&gt; for war!
&gt;
&gt; Fortunately there was only one left, but there were several others
&gt; just like it laying on the ground, as was Bruticus-X, Insecticon and
&gt; Scourge. Cyclonus himself looked heavily damaged as he battled on, the
&gt; look on his face said he was resigned to whatever fate this battle had
&gt; in store for him.
&gt;
&gt; &quot;We are the horde.&quot; the creature said as it raised its arms at
&gt; Cyclonus, its claws out, &quot;You cannot resist us. You will become one
&gt; with us, your technological distinctiveness with strengthen the hive.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; &quot;You are not warrior, you are slaves to a beast! I shall give you what
&gt; you do not deserve, a warrior&#39;s death!&quot; With that he fired, causing
&gt; the creature to back up a step and then the fighting continued.
&gt;
